; Regression test for issue #583: --monthly prices should show last price per
; period, not the sum of all prices within the period.
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/583
;
; When using 'prices' with --monthly (-M), ledger used to incorrectly sum
; prices within a month.  January has two prices ($500.00 and $510.00); the
; correct behavior is to show $510.00 (the last price in January).

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2013/01/05 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $500.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/01/12 Buy more
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $510.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/02/05 Buy again
    Assets:Investments   10 AAPL @ $520.00
    Assets:Cash

test -M prices
2013/01/01 AAPL          $510.00
2013/02/01 AAPL          $520.00
end test
